# Ultracite Rules

This project uses Ultracite for formatting and linting via Biome.

## Key Rules

- Use double quotes for strings in TSX/JSX files
- Use single quotes for strings in TS files
- No unused variables or imports
- Prefer `const` over `let` where possible
- Use TypeScript strict mode
- No explicit `any` types
- Organize imports alphabetically
- No console.log in production code (use console.error/warn for errors)
- Prefer named exports over default exports
- Use `type` imports for type-only imports
